show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/wDYgav
show.description: A girl defies her adoptive parents and returns to her birth family, only to find her place taken by another beloved girl. She is harassed and nearly killed in a car accident. With her dying breath, she vows never to repay anyone’s debts again. Sent back into the past, she faces the same betrayals — but this time, she rises strong and ruthless, ready to claim revenge against all wrongs. Watch "Betrayed Heiress: Vengeance Reborn" now!
